  EffectDiscription_ENG: "Digivolve: 1 from [RizeGreymon][When Digivolving] You may
    play 1 yellow or red Tamer card from your hand without paying its memory cost.
    Then, if [RizeGreymon] or [X Antibody] is in this Digimon\u2019s digivolution
    cards, 1 of your opponent's Digimon gets -2000 DP for the turn for each yellow
    or red Tamer you have in play. [Your Turn] For each Tamer you have in play, this
    Digimon gets +1000 DP."
